FBIS4-380 "drafr069_a_94014" FBIS-AFR-94-069 Daily Report 10 Apr 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Aid Group Reports 8,000 Killed in Kigali Aid Group Reports 8,000 Killed in Kigali LD1004151994 Brussels Radio 1 Network in Dutch 1100 GMT 10 Apr 94 LD1004151994 Brussels Radio 1 Network Dutch BFN [Excerpt] The Medecins Sans Frontieres organization says that in the past few days 8,000 people have been killed in Kigali alone. It is said that throughout Rwanda several tens of thousands of people have been killed in the troubles. Refugees who have crossed the border with Zaire speak of brutal massacres by the government soldiers. [passage omitted]
